        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>et <expan><abbr>Iunon</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> Re<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>inae</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iun</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Secu<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>dus</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>ivitatis</ex></expan> Itiu<supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Viergötterstein einer Jupitersäule; auf den Nebenseiten und der Rückseite Darstellungen der Minerva, des Mercur und des Hercules(?); unterhalb der Inschrift Gigant, der offenbar eine Schrifttafel emporhält. (B): Bauchhenß: Z. 4: de[c(urio)].</p>
            </div>
